title: Senior industry figures amongst first Thoroughbred Horseracing Industries MBA cohort (The University of Liverpool)
text: ( Source : The University of Liverpool ) The University of Liverpool Management School 's Thoroughbred Horseracing Industries MBA welcomed senior managers from across the horseracing industry to its inaugural cohort of part-time students.
